OL,3,CBereaved dad takes on cycling
OL,4,Cchallenge in daughter's memory
OL,6,FThe father of a woman who took her own
OL,7,Flife, is taking on a coast-to-coast
OL,8,Fcycle challenge to raise awareness of
OL,9,Fthe charity which has helped his
OL,10,Ffamily following the tragedy.
OL,12,FIan Logan, 49, is preparing to cycle
OL,13,Fmore than 140 miles from Morecambe to
OL,14,FScarborough over two days this June,
OL,15,Fin aid of Child Bereavement UK.
OL,17,FIt follows the death of his daughter
OL,18,FTamara, 28, who died by suicide last
OL,19,FMay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
