PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779120673
OL,3,CBereaved dad takes on cycling
OL,4,Cchallenge in daughter's memory
OL,6,FIan said Tamara "was just amazing. She
OL,7,Fwas beautiful, funny and caring."
OL,9,FIan and his ex-wife Kirsty are now
OL,10,Fjointly caring for Tamara's four-year-
OL,11,Fold daughter Coral, and said that the
OL,12,Fcharity had supported them through
OL,13,Ftheir grief.
OL,15,FOne of the hardest things they have
OL,16,Fhad to deal with, they said, was how
OL,17,Fto tell their granddaughter that her
OL,18,Fmummy wasn't coming back.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779120673
OL,3,CBereaved dad takes on cycling
OL,4,Cchallenge in daughter's memory
OL,6,FKirsty said: "We rang Child
OL,7,FBereavement and said: 'How do we tell
OL,8,Fthis little girl that her mummy isn't
OL,9,Fhere anymore?'
OL,11,F"Without Child Bereavement's support
OL,12,Fwe wouldn't know what to say to her."
OL,14,FIan added: "They've made an unbearable
OL,15,Fsituation bearable really and they've
OL,16,Ftold us what to say, how to explain
OL,17,Fit, just to make sure we're doing the
OL,18,Fright things for her."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
