CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779120673
OL,3,CBereaved dad takes on cycling
OL,4,Cchallenge in daughter's memory
OL,6,FChild Bereavement UK support grieving
OL,7,Fchildren and young people (up to 25),
OL,8,Fand parents bereaved of a child to
OL,9,Ffind hope and rebuild their lives.
OL,11,F"They've just been a great comfort -
OL,12,Fto know that they're just there when
OL,13,Fwe need them," said Kirsty.
OL,15,F"I've started having counselling with
OL,16,FChild Bereavement UK, my youngest
OL,17,Fdaughter is also having counselling,
OL,18,Fso every penny raised will go to
OL,19,Fhelping families like us.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779120673
OL,3,CBereaved dad takes on cycling
OL,4,Cchallenge in daughter's memory
OL,6,F"And as Coral grows up the need will
OL,7,Fbe so massive that we will have to
OL,8,Fkeep going back to Child Bereavement
OL,9,Ffor help."
OL,11,FIan will be tackling the 140 mile
OL,12,Froute, over 2 days with a group of
OL,13,Ffriends and his brother Andy.
OL,15,F"When Tamara passed away in order to
OL,16,Fkeep my brother busy we started doing
OL,17,Foccasional cycling," said Andy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
