FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779120673
OL,3,CBereaved dad takes on cycling
OL,4,Cchallenge in daughter's memory
OL,6,F"He (Ian) had not been on a bike since
OL,7,Fhe was a boy so it gave us time
OL,8,Ftogether and gave him green space and
OL,9,Fthen he decided he wanted to do a
OL,10,Fchallenge, so that challenge that we
OL,11,Fdecided on was Coast to Coast."
OL,13,FThe route will take them from
OL,14,FMorecambe to Scarborough - where the
OL,15,Ffamily last holidayed before Tamara's
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,F"Its going to be very emotional for
OL,19,Feverybody, for all of us but what
OL,20,Fthey're doing is just fantastic.
OL,26,@nD@EpmnD@Ipn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779120673
OL,3,CBereaved dad takes on cycling
OL,4,Cchallenge in daughter's memory
OL,6,F"And we just hope that it helps raise
OL,7,Fawareness first and foremost - that
OL,8,Fthe charity is there and it is there
OL,9,Fto help families like us, and if we
OL,10,Fcan give a little bit back that's even
OL,11,Fbetter."
OL,13,FThey are hoping Coral will cycle the
OL,14,Flast stretch with her grandad Ian as
OL,15,Fthey arrive into Scarborough.
OL,17,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,18,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,19,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,20,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
